text: Gabriele Sella (15 April 1963 - 2 June 2010) was an Italian cyclist. He competed in the sprint event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1963 births Category:2010 deaths Category:Italian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Italy Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Veneto
